               <p>Second count the same offence as the former, only stating it to be in the dwelling house of 
               <persName id="t18070916-5-person90">
                  Thomas 
                  Sizer
               <interp inst="t18070916-5-person90" type="surname" value="Sizer"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070916-5-person90" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
